CREATE TABLE #PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_DB_DWH_STAGE.#PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_SCH_CLIENTES.TBL_TMP_CLIEN_INH_PLANES_IOT ( COD_PROVEEDOR CHARACTER VARYING(50), COD_EMPRESA CHARACTER VARYING(50), TMCODE CHARACTER VARYING(50), COD_PASE CHARACTER VARYING(50), DES_FASE CHARACTER VARYING(50), BAN_ESTADO CHARACTER VARYING(50), FEC_REGISTRO DATE ) DISTRIBUTE ON RANDOM;

INSERT INTO #PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_DB_DWH_STAGE.#PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_SCH_CLIENTES.TBL_TMP_CLIEN_INH_PLANES_IOT ( COD_PROVEEDOR, COD_EMPRESA, TMCODE, COD_PASE, DES_FASE, BAN_ESTADO, FEC_REGISTRO ) VALUES ( :PROVIDER_ID, :ENTERPRISE_ID, :TMCODE, :PLAN_ID, :FASE, :ESTADO, :FECHA_REGISTRO );
SELECT PROVIDER_ID, ENTERPRISE_ID, TMCODE, PLAN_ID, FASE, ESTADO, FECHA_REGISTRO, USUARIO_BD FROM SYSADM.INH_PLANES_IOT

UPDATE #PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_DWH_DB.#PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_SCH_CLIENTES.TBL_DIM_PLANES_IOT_T1 A SET COD_PROVEEDOR = B.COD_PROVEEDOR ,COD_EMPRESA = B.COD_EMPRESA ,TMCODE = B.TMCODE ,DES_TMCODE = B.DES_TMCODE ,COD_PASE = B.COD_PASE ,DES_FASE = B.DES_FASE ,BAN_ESTADO = B.BAN_ESTADO ,FEC_REGISTRO = B.FEC_REGISTRO ,FEC_ACTUALIZACION_DWH = NOW() FROM (SELECT B.COD_PROVEEDOR ,B.COD_EMPRESA ,B.TMCODE ,NVL(T3.PLAN_DESC,'NO DEFINIDO') DES_TMCODE ,B.COD_PASE ,B.DES_FASE ,B.BAN_ESTADO ,B.FEC_REGISTRO ,NOW() AS FEC_ACTUALIZACION_DWH FROM #PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_DB_DWH_STAGE.#PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_SCH_CLIENTES.TBL_TMP_CLIEN_INH_PLANES_IOT B LEFT JOIN #PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_DWH_DB.#PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_SCH_CLIENTES.TBL_DIM_PLANES_T2 T3 ON B.TMCODE = T3.TMCODE AND B.COD_PASE = T3.COD_PASE AND T3.MC_ACTUA =1 INNER JOIN #PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_DWH_DB.#PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_SCH_CLIENTES.TBL_DIM_PLANES_IOT_T1 A ON (A.COD_PROVEEDOR = B.COD_PROVEEDOR AND A.COD_EMPRESA = B.COD_EMPRESA AND A.TMCODE = B.TMCODE AND A.COD_PASE = B.COD_PASE ) WHERE B.DES_FASE <> A.DES_FASE OR B.BAN_ESTADO <> A.BAN_ESTADO OR B.FEC_REGISTRO <> A.FEC_REGISTRO OR T3.PLAN_DESC <> A.DES_TMCODE ) B WHERE A.COD_PROVEEDOR = B.COD_PROVEEDOR AND A.COD_EMPRESA = B.COD_EMPRESA AND A.TMCODE = B.TMCODE AND A.COD_PASE = B.COD_PASE;

INSERT INTO #PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_DWH_DB.#PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_SCH_CLIENTES.TBL_DIM_PLANES_IOT_T1 SELECT ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY A.COD_PROVEEDOR NULLS LAST,A.COD_EMPRESA NULLS LAST,A.TMCODE NULLS LAST,A.COD_PASE NULLS LAST) + A.MAXSKEY AS SK_PLANES_IOT ,A.COD_PROVEEDOR ,A.COD_EMPRESA ,A.TMCODE ,A.DES_TMCODE ,A.COD_PASE ,A.DES_FASE ,A.BAN_ESTADO ,A.FEC_REGISTRO ,NOW() AS FEC_CARGA_DWH ,NULL AS FEC_ACTUALIZACION_DWH FROM ( SELECT DISTINCT MAXSKEY.SK_PLANES_IOT AS MAXSKEY ,T1.COD_PROVEEDOR ,T1.COD_EMPRESA ,T1.TMCODE ,NVL(T3.PLAN_DESC,'NO DEFINIDO') DES_TMCODE ,T1.COD_PASE ,T1.DES_FASE ,T1.BAN_ESTADO ,T1.FEC_REGISTRO FROM #PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_DB_DWH_STAGE.#PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_SCH_CLIENTES.TBL_TMP_CLIEN_INH_PLANES_IOT T1 LEFT JOIN #PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_DWH_DB.#PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_SCH_CLIENTES.TBL_DIM_PLANES_T2 T3 ON T1.TMCODE = T3.TMCODE AND T1.COD_PASE = T3.COD_PASE AND T3.MC_ACTUA =1 LEFT JOIN #PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_DWH_DB.#PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_SCH_CLIENTES.TBL_DIM_PLANES_IOT_T1 T2 ON (T2.COD_PROVEEDOR = T1.COD_PROVEEDOR AND T2.COD_EMPRESA = T1.COD_EMPRESA AND T2.TMCODE = T1.TMCODE AND T2.COD_PASE = T1.COD_PASE ) INNER JOIN (SELECT NVL(MAX(SK_PLANES_IOT), 0) SK_PLANES_IOT FROM #PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_DWH_DB.#PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_SCH_CLIENTES.TBL_DIM_PLANES_IOT_T1 WHERE SK_PLANES_IOT > 0 ) MAXSKEY ON 1 = 1 WHERE T2.SK_PLANES_IOT IS NULL ) A ;

INSERT INTO #PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_DWH_DB.#PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_SCH_CLIENTES.TBL_DIM_PLANES_IOT_T1 SELECT -1, 'NO DEFINIDO', 'NO DEFINIDO', 'NO DEFINIDO', 'NO DEFINIDO', 'NO DEFINIDO','NO DEFINIDO','NO DEFINIDO',to_date ('1990-01-01 00:00:00','YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS') , CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, CURRENT_TIMESTAMP WHERE NOT EXISTS (SELECT * FROM #PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_DWH_DB.#PRY_DWH.V_0772_SISNOT_SCH_CLIENTES.TBL_DIM_PLANES_IOT_T1 A WHERE A.SK_PLANES_IOT = -1)
